<doc id="1271226" wikidata="Q737253" url="?curid=1271226" title="Petur Alberg">
<text>Petur Alberg (15 December 1885 – 1940) was a Faroese violin player and songwriter from Tórshavn. He composed the anthem of the Faroes, &quot;Mítt alfagra land&quot;, or &quot;Tú alfagra land mítt&quot;, as it is usually called.

