* &quot;Secrets from the Sun&quot; (Inner City, 1977)
* &quot;Without a Song&quot; (Inner City, 1978)
* &quot;The Shadow&quot; (Cheetah, 1990)
* &quot;Feelin&#x27; Good!&quot; (Big City, 2001)
* &quot;Come and See&quot; with Jimmy Ponder (Explore, 2007)

